  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200990/extras/bdebbd32f29b25c61d3d5b7895056511.avif?t=1687787381\" width=495 height=207 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chaotic Multiplayer Madness</h2>Engage in intense battles with up to 4 players, either solo or in teams. Experience a fast-paced onslaught fueled by pure chaos and adrenaline.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Over 50 Unique Weapons</h2>Master a vast arsenal of more than 50 weapons, each with its own mechanics and playstyle. Unleash devastating firepower and outmaneuver your opponents with tactical precision.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200990/extras/d0ba38092e703e40000cfb81fa9aeffa.poster.avif?t=1687787381\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200990/extras/d0ba38092e703e40000cfb81fa9aeffa.webm?t=1687787381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200990/extras/d0ba38092e703e40000cfb81fa9aeffa.mp4?t=1687787381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tactical Gameplay and Skill-Based Combat</h2>Test your skills and cunning as you strategically navigate dynamic arenas. Show off your reflexes and precision in intense, skill-based combat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200990/extras/5e8f588b3642c65b8ffa44bde2c3da78.poster.avif?t=1687787381\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200990/extras/5e8f588b3642c65b8ffa44bde2c3da78.webm?t=1687787381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200990/extras/5e8f588b3642c65b8ffa44bde2c3da78.mp4?t=1687787381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unpredictable Environments</h2>Explore diverse and treacherous environments, from neon-lit cityscapes to untamed jungles. Adapt to the ever-changing landscapes and utilize them to your advantage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200990/extras/85d34a1d5bcc6e933ab487b796459bb4.poster.avif?t=1687787381\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200990/extras/85d34a1d5bcc6e933ab487b796459bb4.webm?t=1687787381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200990/extras/85d34a1d5bcc6e933ab487b796459bb4.mp4?t=1687787381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Teamwork and Rivalries</h2>Form alliances with friends or go solo to prove your dominance. Forge dynamic team dynamics or betray your teammates for personal glory.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlockables and Customization</h2>Progress through the game to unlock new weapons, skins, and customization options. Personalize your character and make a statement on the battlefield.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200990/extras/42b1746bef455e186b4b8b9efed5a5d8.poster.avif?t=1687787381\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200990/extras/42b1746bef455e186b4b8b9efed5a5d8.webm?t=1687787381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200990/extras/42b1746bef455e186b4b8b9efed5a5d8.mp4?t=1687787381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Are you ready to embrace the chaos and dominate the battlefield? Gather your friends, prepare your tactics, and get ready for Trigger Fever! Wishlist now and be among the first to experience the adrenaline-fueled mayhem.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200990/extras/8d00ff29d5a3b303b057d98a30f8edcc.avif?t=1687787381\" width=600 height=144 /></span><br><br>Remember, in Trigger Fever, chaos is your ally. Embrace the madness, hone your skills, and annihilate your opponents with style and flair. Are you ready to enter the fray and become the ultimate champion of Trigger Fever? Let the chaos begin!",
