you ready to embrace the chaos and dominate the battlefield? Gather your friends, prepare your tactics, and get ready for Trigger Fever! Wishlist now and be among the first to experience the adrenaline-fueled mayhem.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200990/extras/8d00ff29d5a3b303b057d98a30f8edcc.avif?t=1687787381\" width=600 height=144 /></span><br><br>Remember, in Trigger Fever, chaos is your ally. Embrace the madness, hone your skills, and annihilate your opponents with style and flair. Are you ready to enter the fray and become the ultimate champion of Trigger Fever? Let the chaos begin!",
